The U.S.-Kenya SME Trade Initiative, signed by the Corporate Council on Africa (CCA) and Kenya Private Sector Alliance (KEPSA) on October 11th 2021, is an initiative to empower Kenyan SMEs to take full advantage of the African Growth and Opportunity Act (AGOA) and be prepared to effectively leverage any future trade agreement between the U.S. and Kenya. Read on.  VISIT ALLAFRiCA'S CCA PAGE